PN,32701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1782841690
OL,3,CGolden eagle found with 17 shotgun
OL,4,Cpellets lodged in her body and wings
OL,6,FA four-year-old female golden eagle
OL,7,Fhas been found with at least 17
OL,8,Fshotgun pellets lodged in her body and
OL,9,Fwings.
OL,11,FSqueagle was moved from the Outer
OL,12,FHebrides to the Lammermuir Hills in
OL,13,Fthe Borders in February 2026, as part
OL,14,Fof a project from Restoring Upland
OL,15,FNature (RUN).
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
