FL,328,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1782841690
OL,3,CGolden eagle found with 17 shotgun
OL,4,Cpellets lodged in her body and wings
OL,6,FThe bird is fitted with a satellite
OL,7,Ftag which tracks her movements, and
OL,8,Fhas travelled through parts of
OL,9,Fnorthern England, including
OL,10,FNorthumberland, the Pennines and the
OL,11,FYorkshire Dales since her release.
OL,13,FOn Monday 1 June, gamekeepers on a
OL,14,FLammermuirs estate noticed the
OL,15,Fcreature "behaving unusually", and got
OL,16,Fin contact with RUN.
OL,18,FSqueagle was collected and taken to
OL,19,Fthe Scottish SPCA's National Wildlife
OL,20,FRescue Centre at Fishcross for
OL,21,Fassessment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,328,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1782841690
OL,3,CGolden eagle found with 17 shotgun
OL,4,Cpellets lodged in her body and wings
OL,6,FA photograph taken in Northumberland
OL,7,Fon Monday 4 May showed significant
OL,8,Fdamage to her wing feathers.
OL,10,FSubsequent scans and treatment
OL,11,Frevealed the eagle had been shot, with
OL,12,Fat least 17 shotgun pellets lodged in
OL,13,Fher body and wings. It is believed the
OL,14,Finjuries were not recent, as the
OL,15,Fwounds had already healed.
OL,17,FPolice Scotland is now appealing for
OL,18,Finformation about the injuries.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
