OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,328,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1782841690
OL,3,CGolden eagle found with 17 shotgun
OL,4,Cpellets lodged in her body and wings
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant David Lynn,
OL,7,FNational Wildlife Crime Coordinator
OL,8,Fsaid: "This was a serious attack on a
OL,9,Fprotected bird of prey which I utterly
OL,10,Fcondemn.
OL,12,F"Thanks to the quick actions of those
OL,13,Fwho reported concerns, the golden
OL,14,Feagle was able to receive specialist
OL,15,Ftreatment and has since been returned
OL,16,Fto the wild. We are working with
OL,17,Fpartners across Scotland and northern
OL,18,FEngland to establish where and when
OL,19,Fshe was shot.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,328,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1782841690
OL,3,CGolden eagle found with 17 shotgun
OL,4,Cpellets lodged in her body and wings
OL,6,F"Following treatment by veterinary
OL,7,Fspecialists at the Scottish SPCA,
OL,8,FSqueagle was released back into the
OL,9,Fwild on Saturday, 6 June, 2026. Her
OL,10,Fcondition will continue to be
OL,11,Fmonitored through observations and
OL,12,Fdetailed analysis of satellite
OL,13,Ftracking."
OL,15,FAnyone with information has been asked
OL,16,Fto get in contact with Police
OL,17,FScotland, quoting incident number 1361
OL,18,Fof 5 June 2026.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
